# Input

```scss
@use"sass:math";

@use "theme"as *;

@use
"library/buttons"
as
buttons;

@use "theme"with(
$primary:blue !default,
$spacing: 8px
);

@use "theme"with($x: red);

@use "theme" with ($primary: blue);

@use "theme" with ($x: red);

@use "theme" as theme with(
$primary:blue
);

```


# Formatted

```scss
@use "sass:math";

@use "theme" as *;

@use "library/buttons" as buttons;

@use "theme" with($primary: blue !default, $spacing: 8px);

@use "theme" with($x: red);

@use "theme" with (
	$primary: blue
);

@use "theme" with (
	$x: red
);

@use "theme" as theme with($primary: blue);

```
